org.mapdb

Class LongMap<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mapdb.LongMap<V>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LongConcurrentHashMap, LongConcurrentLRUMap, LongHashMap

    public abstract class LongMap<V>
extends Object
    Same as 'java.util.Map' but uses primitive 'long' keys to minimise boxing (and GC) overhead.
    Author:
    Jan Kotek
